query: SELECT dusun from kartu_ibu_registration where userID='user12' group by dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as k1_bulan_lalu FROM kartu_anc_registration inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_anc_registration.KiId = kartu_ibu_registration.KiId where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_anc_registration.submissiondate between '2015-01-01' and '2015-10-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as K1_bulan FROM kartu_anc_registration inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_anc_registration.KiId = kartu_ibu_registration.KiId where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_anc_registration.submissiondate between '2015-11-01' and '2015-11-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as K4_bulan_lalu FROM kartu_anc_visit inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_anc_visit.kiId = kartu_ibu_registration.KiId where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_anc_visit.ancKe ='4' and kartu_anc_visit.submissiondate between '2015-01-01' and '2015-10-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa,count(*) as Resiko_bulan_lalu   FROM kartu_anc_registration inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_anc_registration.KiId = kartu_ibu_registration.KiId where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_anc_registration.highRiskPregnancyProteinEnergyMalnutrition = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.malariaRisk = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskLabourTBRisk = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.HighRiskPregnancyTooManyChildren = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.HighRiskPregnancyAbortus = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.HighRiskLabourSectionCesareaRecord = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskSTIBBVs = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskEctopicPregnancy = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.otherRiskMolaHidatidosa = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.otherRiskCongenitalAbnormality = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.otherRiskEarlyWaterbreak = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskCardiovascularDiseaseRecord = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskDidneyDisorder = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskHeartDisorder = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskAsthma = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskTuberculosis = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskMalaria = 'yes' or kartu_anc_registration.highRiskHIVAIDS = 'yes' and kartu_ibu_registration.submissiondate between '2015-01-01' and '2015-10-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun
